OL,3,CSNP Westminster leader demands urgent
OL,4,Creview of UK's 'anti-business policies'
OL,6,FThe UK Government is being challenged
OL,7,Fto launch an "urgent review" of "anti-
OL,8,Fbusiness policies", with the new SNP
OL,9,FWestminster leader saying measures
OL,10,Fsuch as the hike in employers'
OL,11,Fnational insurance contributions
OL,12,Fshould be "scrapped as soon as
OL,13,Fpossible".
OL,15,FDave Doogan made the demand as he
OL,16,Fpledged he would be an "unashamedly
OL,17,Fpro-business voice in the UK
OL,18,FParliament".
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@\O]oD@aOUpD@RO]tD@KOUuD@IO]xD@
OL,26,AXOUzD@KO]
