OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779066195
OL,3,CSNP Westminster leader demands urgent
OL,4,Creview of UK's 'anti-business policies'
OL,6,FHe spoke after taking on the job
OL,7,Ffollowing his predecessor Stephen
OL,8,FFlynn being elected as an MSP in the
OL,9,Frecent Scottish Parliament election.
OL,11,FMr Doogan insisted that "damaging
OL,12,FLabour government policies", including
OL,13,Fthe rise in employers' national
OL,14,Finsurance charges and the "punitive
OL,15,Ftax regime" in the North Sea, are
OL,16,F"hammering businesses and destroying
OL,17,Fthousands of Scottish jobs".
OL,19,FThe SNP MP said: "They must be
OL,20,Furgently reviewed ` and scrapped as
OL,21,Fsoon as possible."
OL,26,@sD@YOUtD@[O]vD@[OUwD@KO]xD@AOUyD@[O]{D@
OL,26,AROU}D@RO]
