OL,3,CSNP Westminster leader demands urgent
OL,4,Creview of UK's 'anti-business policies'
OL,6,FWith the latest figures showing the
OL,7,FUK's unemployment rate is 4.9%,
OL,8,Fcompared with 4.2% when Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer's party came to power in 2024,
OL,10,FMr Doogan said that under Labour
OL,11,Fjoblessness has risen to a five-year
OL,12,Fhigh.
OL,14,FAnd while job vacancies have
OL,15,F"collapsed" he said the cost of living
OL,16,Fhad "soared" at the same time as the
OL,17,FUK's economic growth "has been
OL,18,Fdowngraded and public finances have
OL,19,Fdeteriorated".
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@KO]xD@EOUxD@LO]yD@VOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
