OL,3,CSNP Westminster leader demands urgent
OL,4,Creview of UK's 'anti-business policies'
OL,6,FMr Doogan insisted: "That is a direct
OL,7,Fconsequence of the Labour government's
OL,8,Fdamaging policies and its failure to
OL,9,Frespond to the challenges we face.
OL,11,F"There are already 300,000 more
OL,12,Funemployed people since the Labour
OL,13,FParty got into power ` and there are
OL,14,Fcredible warnings that another quarter
OL,15,Fof a million could lose their jobs in
OL,16,Fthe next year if they don't act.
OL,18,F"Many good businesses across Scotland
OL,19,Fand the UK are struggling because of
OL,20,Fthe hostile business environment the
OL,21,FUK Government is creating.
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
