OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779066195
OL,3,CSNP Westminster leader demands urgent
OL,4,Creview of UK's 'anti-business policies'
OL,6,F"The national insurance tax hike not
OL,7,Fonly broke a Labour Party election
OL,8,Fpledge but it has also meant fewer
OL,9,Fjobs, less investment and inevitable
OL,10,Fprice rises as increased costs are
OL,11,Fpassed on to consumers."
OL,13,FThe SNP MP vowed: "I will press the UK
OL,14,Fgovernment for real action to support
OL,15,Fbusinesses now, while making the case
OL,16,Fthat the past 20 years of Westminster
OL,17,Ffailure shows why Scotland needs the
OL,18,Ffull powers and fresh start of
OL,19,Findependence."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]uD@SOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
