OL,3,CSNP Westminster leader demands urgent
OL,4,Creview of UK's 'anti-business policies'
OL,6,FScottish Labour finance spokesperson
OL,7,FMichael Marra said: "Dave Doogan and
OL,8,Fthe SNP have a real brass neck to be
OL,9,Fmaking such claims about the UK
OL,10,FGovernment when their own ministers at
OL,11,FHolyrood have such a poor record in
OL,12,Fsupporting businesses in Scotland.
OL,14,F"From the impact of their hike to
OL,15,Fbusiness rates, botched policy like
OL,16,Fthe deposit return scheme, and their
OL,17,Frefusal to support Scotland's
OL,18,Fhospitality industry, their decisions
OL,19,Fare taking a real toll on our economy.
OL,26,@oD@UOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
