PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779066195
OL,3,CSNP Westminster leader demands urgent
OL,4,Creview of UK's 'anti-business policies'
OL,6,F"The SNP must explain what they will
OL,7,Fdo to help businesses in Scotland with
OL,8,Fthe powers they have in Edinburgh,
OL,9,Frather than trying to shift the blame
OL,10,Felsewhere."
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary Peter Kyle said:
OL,13,F"The Budget allowed us to stabilise
OL,14,Fthe economy and deliver support for
OL,15,Ffamilies and businesses and we are
OL,16,Fseeing some welcome signs including
OL,17,F332,000 more people in work than a
OL,18,Fyear ago, while the UK was the fastest
OL,19,Fgrowing economy in the G7 in the first
OL,20,Fquarter of this year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
